<dl id="n41107d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n41" href="#n41107d">N41 (VI.B.33)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n41all.htm#n41107d"> 107(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> mandil of mercy</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">For the <mark>&ldquo;Mandil&rdquo; of mercy</mark> see vol. i. 343. Mandil is a kerchief the Sultan waves. <small> Richard F. Burton, trans. <a name="RBTE3" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#RBTE3"><cite title="source">Supplemental Nights to the Book of the Thousand Nights and a Night</cite></a> (n.d.) V, 31n1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
